OL,3,C'I heard popping': police describe
OL,4,Cnight of Lyra's death
OL,6,FThree police officers who were inside
OL,7,FPSNI Land rovers that came under
OL,8,Fattack during a riot in Derry which
OL,9,Fclaimed the life of Lyra McKee gave
OL,10,Fevidence at her murder trial on
OL,11,FTuesday, June 3.JThe 29-year old
OL,12,Fjournalist and author died after she
OL,13,Fwas struck in the head by a bullet as
OL,14,Fshe stood beside a police Landrover
OL,15,Fparked on Fanad Drive observing the
OL,16,Friot in the Creggan Estate on the
OL,17,Fevening of April 18, 2019.JThe New IRA
OL,18,Fclaimed responsibility for her murder.
